      "text": "This is a LibraVox recording. All LibraVox recordings are in the public domain.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-001",
      "start": 6.66,
      "end": 12.6,
      "text": "For more information or to volunteer, please visit LibraVox.org.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-002",
      "start": 13.92,
      "end": 17.54,
      "text": "ASOP's Fables. The Ass and the Old Peasant.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-003",
      "start": 18.88,
      "end": 23.58,
      "text": "An old peasant was sitting in a meadow watching his ass, which was grazing close by.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-004",
      "start": 24.28,
      "end": 27.94,
      "text": "When all of a sudden he caught sight of armed men stealthily approaching.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-005",
      "start": 28.62,
      "end": 33.18,
      "text": "He jumped up in a moment and begged the Ass to fly with him as fast as he could.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-006",
      "start": 33.76,
      "end": 37.06,
      "text": "Or else, said he, we shall both be captured by the enemy.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-007",
      "start": 37.92,
      "end": 40.32,
      "text": "But the Ass just looked round lazily and said,",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-008",
      "start": 40.92,
      "end": 45.56,
      "text": "And if so, do you think they'll make me carry heavier loads than I have to now?",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-009",
      "start": 46.4,
      "end": 47.84,
      "text": "No, said his master.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-010",
      "start": 48.9,
      "end": 50.6,
      "text": "Oh well then, said the Ass.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-011",
      "start": 51.06,
      "end": 54.44,
      "text": "I don't mind if they do take me, for I shan't be any worse off.",
      "note": ""
    },
    {
      "id": "line-012",
      "start": 55.44,
      "end": 59.54,
      "text": "End of the Ass and the Old Peasant.",
      "note": ""
    }
  ],
